                      <span>40</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-12-15</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I'm giving this book to 10 middle managers - while initially they'll probably think it's childish, once they read it they will understand why they received it. Seuss gives us all a simplified view of life and applying the basics to home and work. I also highly recommend everyone read "Open Your Mind, Open Your Life: A Little Book of Wisdom" by Taro Gold.</span>
                  
              
